OL,3,CJesy Nelson says national rollout of
OL,4,Cbaby SMA screening is a 'victory'
OL,6,FFormer Little Mix singer Jesy Nelson
OL,7,Fhas welcomed news there will be a
OL,8,Fnational rollout of spinal muscular
OL,9,Fatrophy (SMA) screening for newborns,
OL,10,Fafter previously describing it as a
OL,11,F"postcode lottery".
OL,13,FNelson began campaigning for newborn
OL,14,Fbabies to be screened after her twins,
OL,15,FOcean Jade and Story Monroe Nelson,
OL,16,Fwere diagnosed with the rare
OL,17,Fcondition, which causes progressive
OL,18,Fmuscle wastage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
