PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784207920
OL,3,CJesy Nelson says national rollout of
OL,4,Cbaby SMA screening is a 'victory'
OL,6,FThe Department of Health announced on
OL,7,FThursday that the national newborn
OL,8,Fscreening programme for SMA will be
OL,9,Frolled out across England as part of
OL,10,Fan evaluation programme from the end
OL,11,Fof this year.
OL,13,FHundreds of thousands of babies will
OL,14,Fbe screened as part of the simple heel
OL,15,Fprick blood test shortly after birth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784207920
OL,3,CJesy Nelson says national rollout of
OL,4,Cbaby SMA screening is a 'victory'
OL,6,FNelson said: "After years of
OL,7,Fcampaigning, it means so much to see
OL,8,Fthe heel prick test for SMA begin
OL,9,Frolling out from October, with
OL,10,Fimplementation continuing throughout
OL,11,F2027 until every newborn screening
OL,12,Flaboratory across the UK is offering
OL,13,Fthe test.
OL,15,F"Today is a day of hope. Knowing that
OL,16,Ffuture families will have access to
OL,17,Fearly diagnosis and the opportunity
OL,18,Ffor the best possible outcomes is
OL,19,Fsomething I'm incredibly proud to have
OL,20,Fsupported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784207920
OL,3,CJesy Nelson says national rollout of
OL,4,Cbaby SMA screening is a 'victory'
OL,6,F"This is a victory for every family
OL,7,Faffected by SMA. Whilst it can't
OL,8,Fchange the future of our children, I
OL,9,Fknow it marks the beginning of a
OL,10,Fbrighter future for future SMA
OL,11,Ffamilies."
OL,13,FIn a post on Instagram last month,
OL,14,Faccompanied by a video of her becoming
OL,15,Femotional, Nelson said a previous
OL,16,Fannouncement that screening would come
OL,17,Fin October was a big milestone but
OL,18,Fwould "only cover 72% of England".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784207920
OL,3,CJesy Nelson says national rollout of
OL,4,Cbaby SMA screening is a 'victory'
OL,6,FShe added: "That means some babies
OL,7,Fwon't be screened simply because of
OL,8,Fwhere they live. A postcode lottery
OL,9,Flike that just isn't fair.
OL,11,F"Every baby deserves the same chance,
OL,12,Fevery baby's life matters."
OL,14,FThe new development means all parts of
OL,15,FEngland will be covered by the
OL,16,Fevaluation, which will inform future
OL,17,Frecommendations on testing newborns by
OL,18,Fthe UK National Screening Committee.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
