PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784207920
OL,3,CJesy Nelson says national rollout of
OL,4,Cbaby SMA screening is a 'victory'
OL,6,FGiles Lomax, chief executive officer
OL,7,Fof Spinal Muscular Atrophy (SMA) UK,
OL,8,Fsaid: "After years of campaigning by
OL,9,Fthe SMA community and our partner
OL,10,Forganisations, this is a hugely
OL,11,Fimportant step forward.
OL,13,F"When newborn screening for SMA begins
OL,14,Flater this year in October, thousands
OL,15,Fof babies will benefit from earlier
OL,16,Fdiagnosis and access to life-changing
OL,17,Ftreatment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784207920
OL,3,CJesy Nelson says national rollout of
OL,4,Cbaby SMA screening is a 'victory'
OL,6,F"We are delighted to see the
OL,7,Fconfirmation that the remaining six
OL,8,Fscreening laboratories will begin
OL,9,Fscreening from October 2027, this
OL,10,Fdemonstrates a clear commitment to
OL,11,Fmaking newborn screening available
OL,12,Facross England.
OL,14,F"No family should face a postcode
OL,15,Flottery when it comes to a condition
OL,16,Fwhere every day without treatment can
OL,17,Flead to irreversible loss of motor
OL,18,Fneurons."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
