PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784207920
OL,3,CJesy Nelson says national rollout of
OL,4,Cbaby SMA screening is a 'victory'
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FSMA can leave babies unable to sit up,
OL,12,Fcrawl or walk. In the most severe
OL,13,Fcases, it stops them breathing or
OL,14,Fswallowing.
OL,16,FEarly treatment, however, can delay
OL,17,Fthe progressive nature of the illness
OL,18,Fand help children live longer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
