FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784207920
OL,3,CJesy Nelson says national rollout of
OL,4,Cbaby SMA screening is a 'victory'
OL,6,FHealth Secretary, James Murray, said:
OL,7,F"No parent should have to watch their
OL,8,Fchild lose the ability to move or
OL,9,Fbreathe, knowing that earlier
OL,10,Ftreatment could have made all the
OL,11,Fdifference.
OL,13,F"This expansion means babies across
OL,14,FEngland will be tested from birth,
OL,15,Fgiving them the best possible chance
OL,16,Fof a full and healthy life, and
OL,17,Fanother step in the right direction as
OL,18,Fwe do all we can to reduce health
OL,19,Finequalities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784207920
OL,3,CJesy Nelson says national rollout of
OL,4,Cbaby SMA screening is a 'victory'
OL,6,F"I'm in awe of the campaigners who've
OL,7,Fworked tirelessly to raise awareness
OL,8,Fof this rare but very serious genetic
OL,9,Fcondition. We're moving faster and
OL,10,Frolling screening out more widely to
OL,11,Fensure children get the best treatment
OL,12,Ffrom the earliest possible moment."
OL,14,FScotland is establishing a similar
OL,15,Fscreening programme drawing on funding
OL,16,Ffrom the private sector.
OL,18,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,19,FCare is taking a similar approach and
OL,20,Fseeking #5 million of investment to
OL,21,Fexpand evaluation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
